reviews.text: Excellent place for family with kids. Can spend all day here with reasonable cost. Public facilities, shops and entertainment are all well designed with kids in mind. The cinema is even decorated and provided with kids seats and play areas. Coming place is more spacious than you could imagine.
Large mall with wide variety of shops, restaurants, and a cinema, but no supermarket. Great place for families with young kids. Parking is relatively cheap.
Good location, family friendly! Good for shopping with kids

A large and well designed shopping mall. Shops were of large types and properly located at different areas of the mall. Food choices were absurd with a bizarre choice from local fast food to American tastes to top-of-the-class cuisines. A huge recommendation for foodies. Activities there are also never-ending and makes the mall suitable for children and adults of all ages.
Spacious.  Good restaurants.  Convenient supermarket.  Comfortable weeknight visit.
